0.3
  * Added 'user' argument for servers where it may be required (liquidsoap,
  etc.). Use 'source' if you are using default Icecast server.
0.2
  * Makefile: rewrite; more packager-friendly
  * man page
  * use getopt() for advanced settings
  * remove "dump file" feature, it is not implemented in libshout. explain
    tee(1) usage instead
  * signal handling to print "total bytes read" stats
  * write all errors to stderr, regular output to stdout. Redirecting output
    to /dev/null makes oggfwd silent, except when errors occur
  * lint + -Wall clean
0.1
  * add advanced features by rafael2k <rafael@riseup.net>
  * initial version
